entry.tran: 我(第一人称单数宾格代词)
entry.def: A speaker or writer uses me to refer to himself or herself. Me is a first person singular pronoun. Me is used as the object of a verb or a preposition.

example.ex: I had to make important decisions that would affect me for the rest of my life...

example.ex: He asked me to go to Cambridge with him...
example.tran: 他要我和他一起去剑桥。
